Order process
---------------------

We will email a dispatch notification to you when your order is en-route. If the delivery method used has tracking available 
then a tracking code will be included in the dispatch notification email.

This email receipt may be used as a VAT invoice, our VAT number can be found towards the top right-hand corner.

If you have any questions about your order please get in touch at support@gimsonrobotics.com, quoting your order number (ID).

Additional information
---------------------

